You enter a deep canyon set directly into the Shadow Swamp. On all sides, swamp water flows or trickles into the canyon, falling over 100 feet to splash in the waters below. Despite the constant influx of dark fluids, the water at the bottom of the canyon never rises and the swamp never drains.
There are few distinguishable features of the building before you. It gives the impression of being massive, but seems to dissolve into the Plane of Shadow itself.
